Interface OWLIndividualList<E extends OWLIndividual>

public interface OWLIndividualList<E extends OWLIndividual>
extends java.util.List<E>

Represents a list of OWLIndividual objects. This interface shouldn't be confused with rdf:List structure (in this library represented by OWLList). The sole purpose of this interface is to add some access respectively update methods that do not exist in List. In addition, it adds insertion methods that realize semantics of sets, i.e., prevention of duplicates.
